description:
Due to change of version name in TST, version text overflows in menu. Fix display:

```
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
  overflow: hidden;
  white-space: nowrap; 
```


![image](/uploads/eb68cb9974451f127a58f4d0907cf269/image.png)

If running FF display info on how to enable container queries

![image](/uploads/6dfbf9fcbed222e7fc8d4ad4104aa987/image.png)


You can check for not supporting container queries like:
```
if (!('container' in document.documentElement.style)) {
 // I do not understand container queries
}
```
https://github.com/GoogleChromeLabs/container-query-polyfill/blob/main/src/index.ts
